ction_btn" href="https://0x72.itch.io/dungeontileset-ii/devlog"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_news" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18" version="1.1"><rect x="1" y="3" width="22" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="6" y1="8" x2="18" y2="8"></line><line x1="6" y1="12" x2="18" y2="12"></line><line x1="6" y1="16" x2="18" y2="16"></line></svg>Devlog</a></li><li><a data-label="related_btn" href="https://itch.io/games-like/309028/dungeontileset-ii" class="action_btn related_games_btn" target="_blank"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_map" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="18" height="18" version="1.1"><polygon points="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"></polygon><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"></line><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"></line></svg> <span class="full_label">More like this</span><span class="mobile_label">Related</span></a></li></ul><script type="text/javascript">new I.GameUserTools('#user_tools')</script><div class="main wrapper game_page_wrapper" id="wrapper"><div class="inner_column size_very_large family_inconsolata" id="inner_column"><div class="header align_left has_image" id="header"><img alt="Pixel art stone wall with three torches mounted on the lower section, each with animated flames." src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE1MTg1NTQuZ2lm/original/mc%2F7UB.gif"/><h1 itemprop="name" class="game_title">16x16 DungeonTileset II</h1></div><div class="view_game_page page_widget base_widget buy_on_top" id="view_game_9691358"><div class="header_buy_row"><p>A downloadable tileset</p><div class="buy_row"><div class="button_message"><a class="button buy_btn" href="https://0x72.itch.io/dungeontileset-ii/purchase">Download Now</a><span class="buy_message"><span class="sub">Name your own price</span></span></div></div></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><p>Hi!</p>
<p><img alt="running zombie" src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE5ODA4NjQuZ2lm/original/Fe49uB.gif" loading="lazy"><br><br></p>
<p>This is a version&nbsp;II of&nbsp;<a href="https://0x72.itch.io/16x16-dungeon-tileset">my first dungeon tileset</a> with some major changes and <a href="https://lospec.com/palette-list/linear-color-palette-basic" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">recolored</a> (<a href="https://grafxkid.tumblr.com/palettes" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">GrafxKid</a>).</p>
<p>As always:</p>
<p>You can use this tileset for whatever you like (<a href="https://www.tldrlegal.com/license/creative-commons-cc0-1-0-universal" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">CC-0</a>).</p>
<p>Credit is not necessary, but if you create something using this tileset I&#x27;d be happy to see your work (you can comment with a link).</p>
<p>That being said, you can still credit me if you feel like :)</p>
<p>- Robert<br><br>OFFICIAL EXTANSION PACKS:</p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://0x72.itch.io/16x16-dungeontileset-ii-sewers">https://0x72.itch.io/16x16-dungeontileset-ii-sewers<br></a>- (in progress)</p>
<p>-----</p>
<p>There was a couple &quot;extension packs&quot; or their versions&nbsp;made by other people (random order):</p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://superdark.itch.io/enchanted-forest-characters">https://superdark.itch.io/enchanted-forest-characters</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://superdark.itch.io/16x16-free-npc-pack">https://superdark.itch.io/16x16-free-npc-pack</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://safwyl.itch.io/16x16-dungeon-autotile-remix">https://safwyl.itch.io/16x16-dungeon-autotile-remix</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/post/423467">https://itch.io/post/423467</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://aekae13.itch.io/16x16-dungeon-walls-reconfig">https://aekae13.itch.io/16x16-dungeon-walls-reconfig</a></p>
<p>- <a href="https://revenger-wizard.itch.io/dungeon-tileset-assets">https://revenger-wizard.itch.io/dungeon-tileset-assets</a> (unity pack made by <a href="http://revenger-wizard.itch.io">wizard</a>)</p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://opengameart.org/content/halloween-characters" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://opengameart.org/content/halloween-characters</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://anritool.itch.io/cr-tileset">https://anritool.itch.io/cr-tileset</a><br></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://omniboy.itch.io/jungle-dungeon-16x16-tileset">https://omniboyok.itch.io/jungle-dungeon-16x16-tileset</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/post/3458260">https://itch.io/post/3458260</a> - taller walls</p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://efetusder.itch.io/smooth-dungeon-tileset">https://efetusder.itch.io/smooth-dungeon-tileset</a>&nbsp;- efetusder version with some new tiles</p>
<p>- <a href="https://nijikokun.itch.io/dungeontileset-ii-extended">https://nijikokun.itch.io/dungeontileset-ii-extended</a> - more tiles more items!<br></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://kosinaz.itch.io/16x16-dark-dungeon-tileset">https://kosinaz.itch.io/16x16-dark-dungeon-tileset</a>&nbsp;- <a href="https://kosinaz.itch.io/">Zoltan Kosina</a>&#x27;s variation</p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/post/7382123">https://itch.io/post/7382123</a>&nbsp;- <a href="https://itch.io/profile/dajeki">Dajeki</a>&#x27;s uniform-sized spritesheets</p>
<p>- <a href="https://keymaster777.itch.io/0x72-dungeon-tileset-2-stairs-extension">https://keymaster777.itch.io/0x72-dungeon-tileset-2-stairs-extension</a> - stairs by <a href="https://itch.io/profile/keymaster777">keymaster777<br></a> </p>
<p>- <a href="https://itch.io/post/12912606">https://itch.io/post/12912606</a> by&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/profile/axeweilder43">axeweilder43</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/post/13639525">https://itch.io/post/1363952</a>&nbsp;dino by&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/profile/hukto-he">hukto-he</a></p>
<p>-&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/post/14696304">https://itch.io/post/14696304</a> -&nbsp;red demon attack by&nbsp;<a href="https://itch.io/profile/gelezo43">gelezo43</a><br>- let know if you feel like I should put a link you your work&nbsp;here as well</p>
<p>-----<br></p>
