_down_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/s-ebi"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/s-ebi">S_ebi</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2025-07-11 21:50:16"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13329791">359 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hey, we used these sprites for our project. We also added many animations to them. You might want to check it out.<br><br><a href="https://lukas74m.itch.io/brawl-of-the-depths">https://lukas74m.itch.io/brawl-of-the-depths</a><br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-13314012" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:11305805,&quot;id&quot;:13314012}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version=