e: inherit" loading="lazy"></a><br></figure>
<p>Hi @0x72 and @Everyone!&nbsp;I&#x27;ve created a<strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://kingbell.itch.io/pixel-sprite-mixer" target="_blank">Sprite Mixer</a></strong>&nbsp;<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE4MjkzMDM3LmdpZg==/original/BdZfVT.gif" loading="lazy"> that includes your characters with customization! Plus animations to&nbsp;easily export as sprite sheets.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-11196722" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:54608,&quot;id&quot;:11196722}" class="community_post is_reply has_replies has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/0x72"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE5NzEwNTEucG5n/25x25%23/rllnE7.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/0x72">0x72</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2024-10-23 20:33:27"><a href="https://itch.io/post/11196722">1 year ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(2 edits)</span> <span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Wow, above and beyond! Amazing!</p>
<p>&lt;3</p>
<p>This is the ultimate pixel character generator!!!!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-11197100" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:11782342,&quot;id&quot;:11197100}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/kingbell"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE4MTUyMDIwLnBuZw==/25x25%23/ZmZd8h.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/kingbell">KingBell🗡️</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2024-10-23 21:22:00"><a href="https://itch.io/post/11197100">1 year ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Thank you! Hope it inspires others to keep creating! Can help with your expansions!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-11156227" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:11819620,&quot;id&quot;:11156227}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/gabrdev1"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/gabrdev1">gabrdev1</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2024-10-18 04:38:19"><a href="https://itch.io/post/11156227">1 year ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>I&#x27;m having problems with the tileset to do my autotiling, does anyone know how can I solve it? (the problem is that I cant undertand how to organize the tiles on autotiling).&nbsp;<br><br>Amazing sprites!!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div id="post-10887016" data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:2321974,&quot;id&quot;:10887016}" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg aria-hidden role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" version="1.1"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/goblin-mode-games"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIwNjU5NzUzLnBuZw==/25x25%23/sr9Bhp.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/goblin-mode-games">Goblin Mode Games</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2024-09-15 13:36:10"><a href="https://itch.io/post/10887016">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>This is a fantastic asset pack, thanks so much for making it available. I used it in my submission to Brackeys Jam 2024, would love if you checked it out!&nbsp;<a href="https://goblin-mode-games.itch.io/storm-the-dungeon">https://goblin-mode-games.itch.io/storm-the-dungeon</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii&amp;intent=community" data-regist